sitemap-validator

Build:
    go build

Run (one or more sitemap URLs):
    ./sitemap-validator https://areena.yle.fi/sitemap.xml
    ./sitemap-validator https://areena.yle.fi/sitemap.xml https://arenan.yle.fi/sitemap.xml

Output (stderr): one line per violation. Exit 0 if valid, exit 1 if any errors.
    <sitemap-url>: <violation>
